And it's better than just locking straight to the parking meter, because in some cases, your U-lock might not fit all the way around.

676
01:02:47,830 --> 01:02:57,936
Or when you lock to only one thing, then the bike is more likely to rotate and fall or whatever and block somebody's access.

677
01:02:58,423 --> 01:03:01,484
Additionally, cable locks are totally ineffective on a parking meter.

678
01:03:02,264 --> 01:03:04,785
